_sText:
Small level with intense fights, wether in interior between shelves, boxes and various warehouses elements, or long range passing through the main street, all type of players will find themselves in this new map making the link between our Warehouse project of 2014 and Seizure (2016) since the playable area is located directly between the grids of the two maps.

Excellent for bloody game types like Deathmatch or Gun-Games, but also warm-up due to its "competitive design like". Even Prop-Hunt players will enjoy playing on this level.
